{"tid":920582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭深切哀悼梁振英：愛國、正氣好榜樣","createTime":"2018-11-29T02:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:11:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"57083046c9ed3f5bb2fc1e9beca7d9d3ce2d2f38","tid":920582,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會委員劉迺強昨晚（21日）因癌病不治逝世，終年71歲。特首林鄭月娥今日對其劉迺強辭世表示深切哀悼；全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英則指「悼念迺強，愛國、正氣的好榜樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2122045/org/85bdd879783a6b24646c2092b590189c.jpg/XrAcVFRV-UJnY2cNOPQvv7qi-OocOVbmkrhloZK4ZaE?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2122045%2Forg%2F85bdd879783a6b24646c2092b590189c.jpg%2FXrAcVFRV-UJnY2cNOPQvv7qi-OocOVbmkrhloZK4ZaE%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=2e73ce4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在聲明稱，劉迺強長期以來積極投入公共和社會服務，展現了對國家和香港的關愛，特別在與《基本法》有關的工作上，他曾在回歸前出任基本法諮詢委員會成員，並自2007年起出任基本法委員會委員，在推廣及研究《基本法》的工作上，貢獻良多：「我對他離世感到難過，謹代表香港特別行政區政府，向他的家人致以深切慰問」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/262064/%E5%8A%89%E8%BF%BA%E5%BC%B7%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%87%E5%93%80%E6%82%BC-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A3%E6%B0%A3%E5%A5%BD%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F262064%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E8%25BF%25BA%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%2593%2580%25E6%2582%25BC-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25A6%259C%25E6%25A8%25A3&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=916e5a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/262064/%E5%8A%89%E8%BF%BA%E5%BC%B7%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%A1%